title: Grateful Dead Live at Irvine Meadows on 1989-04-29
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Walkin' Blues, Brown Eyed Women, Memphis Blues, Built To Last, Blow Away, One More Saturday Night

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Looks Like Rain, He's Gone-> Spoonful-> Drums-> Jam-> I Will Take You Home-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues
